<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Para mi amor ❤️</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ff758c, #ff7eb3);
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .mensaje {
            position: absolute;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            z-index: 2;
            animation: aparecer 2s ease-in-out;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #e91e63;
            font-size: 3em;
        }

        p {
            color: #444;
            font-size: 1.4em;
        }

        .corazon {
            position: absolute;
            color: red;
            animation: caer linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes caer {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(-10vh);
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(110vh);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        @keyframes aparecer {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.5); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        }

        button {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            background: #e91e63;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 1em;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #d81b60;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="mensaje">
        <h1>❤️ Te Amo Mi Amor ❤️</h1>
        <p>Desde que llegaste a mi vida, todo es más bonito ✨</p>
        <p>Eres mi felicidad, mi paz y mi persona favorita 💖</p>
        <button onclick="alert('Siempre serás lo mejor de mi vida ❤️')">Haz clic aquí 💌</button>
    </div>

    <audio autoplay loop>
        <source src="https://www.bensound.com/bensound-music/bensound-romantic.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
    </audio>

    <script>
        function crearCorazon() {
            const corazon = document.createElement("div");
            corazon.classList.add("corazon");
            corazon.innerHTML = "❤️";
            corazon.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + "vw";
            corazon.style.fontSize = Math.random() * 20 + 20 + "px";
            corazon.style.animationDuration = Math.random() * 3 + 2 + "s";

            document.body.appendChild(corazon);

            setTimeout(() => {
                corazon.remove();
            }, 5000);
        }

        setInterval(crearCorazon, 250);
    </script>

</body>
</html>